Transcription.Text: The right lay the pillars of the hall entrance. Ahead was a solid, five- barred gate, painted white, with the familiar Whitescar blazoning the top bar. Beyond this, the track lifted itself up a gentle rise of pasture, and # vanished over a ridge.
